OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day expected today with
OL,6,Fspells of sunshine, although perhaps
OL,7,Fcloudier than Tuesday, potentially
OL,8,Fdeveloping into sea fog near coasts.
OL,9,FStaying warm, especially in the south
OL,10,Fof the region with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome cloud lingering
OL,13,Fovernight, which may bring some light
OL,14,Fdrizzle on higher hills. A mild night
OL,15,Fexpected with some places not dropping
OL,16,Fbelow double figures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
