OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA cooler and more changeable
OL,6,Fday on Thursday, with a band of rain
OL,7,Fmoving eastwards through the morning.
OL,8,FClearing in the afternoon but sunny
OL,9,Fspells and showers continue.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,12,Funsettled on Friday and Saturday with
OL,13,Ffurther rain at times, mainly on
OL,14,FSaturday. Turning more showery again
OL,15,Fon Sunday. Temperatures nearer to
OL,16,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
